Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a jamun tree which was on a bank of a river.
In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his Wife... One day the crocodile came to the bank of the river
and rested under the tree. The kind hearted monkey offered him some food. The crocodile came back the next day
for more fruits,as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good friends...  

